<p><span style="color: #3f7dba;">A : </span>Do you possibly have <span style="color: #f5b041;">hand warmers</span>?</p>
<p><span style="color: #3f7dba;">A : </span>My <span style="color: #f5b041;">hands</span> are freezing.</p>
<p><span style="color: #d16821;">B : </span>Yes, but you have to be <span style="color: #f5b041;">careful</span>.</p>
<p><span style="color: #d16821;">B : </span>You might <span style="color: #f5b041;">burn</span> yourself.</p>

